nodes.text: The Gaalt Sky Rowing team was a sporting team from the Gaalt system. Author Skreen, the technical director of the Manifold Mollusk Matrix and Matrimony Association, was a member of the Sky Rowing team.

The Gaalt Sky Rowing team was mentioned in a profile for Skreen, a character featured in Monsters and Aliens from George Lucas, a book published in 1993. Lucasfilm employee Leland Chee, who maintains the Holocron continuity database, has indicated that information contained in the book is non-canonical.
